The Premier League returns this weekend following fixtures in domestic competitions. On Saturday, Arsenal travel to Crystal Palace in the early kick-off. Chelsea host Burnley, Southampton travel to Leicester City and Manchester United take on Norwich at Old Trafford. The late kick-off will see Liverpool away at Tottenham Hotspur. Saturday, January 11
